s/:pda\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 404 for unknown PDA\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mHTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mGET /health\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns 200 with expected fields\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mHTTP endpoint tests\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mGET /health\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreflects unsettled round count\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/player-stats.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPlayer stats + streaks\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns zero stats for empty history\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/player-stats.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPlayer stats + streaks\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns zero streaks for empty history\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/player-stats.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPlayer stats + streaks\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreturns empty game breakdown for empty history\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/player-stats.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPlayer stats + streaks\u001b[2m > \u001b[22m3 consecutive wins → current=3 best=3\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/player-stats.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPlayer stats + streaks\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mwin-win-loss-win → current=1 best=2\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m src/__tests__/player-stats.test.ts\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mPlayer stats + streaks\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mrefund entry is skipped in streak calculation\nservices/backend test: \u001b[31m\u001b[1m\u001b[7m FAIL \u001b[27m\u0